---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Sight Words"
  description="Learn about this free sight word website for parents, teachers, and children."
  canonicalUrl="https://sightwordspractice.com/about"
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About</h1>

  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
    This website is a free sight word learning tool with flashcards, word lists, and printable resources. It is made
    to help children build reading confidence through clear, simple practice.
  </p>

  <section class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Who It Is For</h2>
      <p>
        The site is designed for parents, teachers, tutors, and children who need an easy way to practice high-frequency
        sight words at home or in the classroom.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Why This Site Exists</h2>
      <p>
        Learning tools should be simple to access. This site exists to provide useful sight word practice without
        sign-up steps, account creation, or extra barriers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Simple and Accessible by Design</h2>
      <p>
        Pages are built to be clear, readable, and quick to use on phones, tablets, and computers. The goal is to make
        sight word practice straightforward so families and educators can focus on learning, not setup.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">No Sign-Up Required</h2>
      <p>
        You can use the flashcards, word lists, and print resources right away. No account, login, or personal
        information is required.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
